          <p class="text-gray-700 font-lato font-light leading-relaxed mb-4">Trucks are the backbone of Australian industry — from the local courier in a Toyota HiAce to long-haul operators running Kenworth prime movers across the Nullarbor. The commercial vehicle market in Australia is significant, with thousands of new trucks sold every month across all categories. Whether you are a sole trader adding your first light commercial vehicle or a transport company expanding a fleet, the right finance structure can deliver substantial tax savings and cash flow benefits.</p>
