        <section class="mb-16">
          <h2 class="font-montserrat font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl text-[#1e3a5f] mb-6">Truck Finance Rates (February 2026)</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 font-lato font-light leading-relaxed mb-4">Truck finance rates vary by vehicle type, age, finance amount, and your business strength. Indicative ranges with the RBA at 3.85%:</p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 my-6">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#10b981] mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
